turally and physically denied, the place which is not.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aDomestic fiction, EnglishxHistory and criticism. 0aEnglish fictiony19th centuryxHistory and criticism. 0aFamily violence in literature. 0aHuman body in literature. 4aLiterature : English Literature. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / English, Irish, Scottish, Welsh.2bisacsh1 aShakinovsky, Lynn, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791488621423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791488621/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles